0.02
----
- Change Add buttons that redirect to URL to code to create a new item
- Allow URL links to be clickable
- Automatically open the Edit form of the new publication after creation
- Publications Index
  - Flag Rush Publications
  - Flag Upcoming Publications (on Publication as well)
  - Allow Multiple Filters
  - Prevent a Due Date of < 5 Days from now
  - Multiple Views
    - View 1:
      - Report #, Report Type, Status, Due Date, Assigned To
    - View 2:
      - Report #, Report Type, Title, Authors, Status, Due Date, Cost Centre, Project Code
